{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775899793663,"sessionID":"ses_284209335ffeGezUdA84JigjjI","part":{"id":"prt_d7be054d5001gIF2YYTvj0pRe1","messageID":"msg_d7be014a2001qeF2DHw4fcjHdN","sessionID":"ses_284209335ffeGezUdA84JigjjI","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/cli/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/cli/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-025 — MetadataService and Data Models\n2: \n3: > **Module:** `cmd/cli`\n4: > **Language:** Python\n5: > **Size:** M\n6: > **Stage:** ST-3 (Design) Completed → ST-4 (Implementation)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## ST-4.1 — AgentMetadata Model Enhancement\n11: \n12: ### Tasks\n13: \n14: | # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n15: |---|------|--------------|------|\n16: | 4.1.1 | Add `model_config` to `AgentMetadata` with `populate_by_name=True`, `validate_assignment=True`, `extra='forbid'` | Unit test: extra fields raise ValidationError | 0.5h |\n17: | 4.1.2 | Add field `pack_timestamp: Optional[str]` with description \"ISO timestamp of pack operation\" | Unit test: field serializes/deserializes correctly | 0.5h |\n18: | 4.1.3 | Add field `dockerfile_generated: Optional[bool]` with description \"Whether Dockerfile was generated\" | Unit test: field serializes/deserializes correctly | 0.5h |\n19: | 4.1.4 | Verify `language` validator accepts lowercase/uppercase, rejects invalid values | Unit test: \"Python\"→\"python\", \"invalid\" raises ValueError | 0.5h |\n20: | 4.1.5 | Verify `build_mode` validator accepts lowercase/uppercase, rejects invalid values | Unit test: \"Local\"→\"local\", \"invalid\" raises ValueError | 0.5h |\n21: | 4.1.6 | Verify `port` validator rejects ports outside 1-65535 | Unit test: 0 raises ValueError, 65536 raises ValueError, 8080 passes